title: Pro-Death Ravers
text:
Pro-Death Ravers is the second album by the Danish band <a href="Psychopomps%20%28band%29">Psychopomps</a>. It was originally released in 1993 and differs greatly from their previous release. This album has a greater focus on guitars and less focus on synthesizers.
Personnel.
Jesper Schmidt: Vox, Programming, Keyboards <br>
Flemming Norre Larsen: Programming, Lyrics
